Summary: Teardrop UFO in Local Iowa Neighborhood
divs: Sighting Details1. Just came into my bedroom. All lights off to go to bed. Walking by thewindow. 2. Stranger than usual lights outside. 3. Exactly what I came here totell you. A UFO. 4. Stared at it. Seemed to notice that I was watching it. Likeit could feel my presence. Felt a tingle go through my right arm. Felt verycalm. Even to this day I can hardly become afraid of things. 5. Teardrop shaped.Black body, silver top with yellow light at tip. row of lights toward the base.green and blue lights. rotated around the object. It hovered. Then shot a yellowstream of light that went to the right of my house. Then the Object shotstraight up breaking off a branch of my tree which is still noticable. 6. Shotstraight up and out of sight. Think abductions have taken place after this. Havenot told parents because i do not want them to think i am crazy. or to worryabout me.
